  - atc_2: Lidocaine is in the therapeutic group of ophthalmologicals and antipruritics, incl. antihistamines, anesthetics, etc. and throat preparations and cardiac therapy and otologicals and anesthetics and vasoprotectives.
  - atc_3: Lidocaine is pharmacologically related to local anesthetics and antipruritics, incl. antihistamines, anesthetics, etc. and throat preparations and antiarrhythmics, class i and iii and other otologicals and anesthetics, local and agents for treatment of hemorrhoids and anal fissures for topical use.
